{
  "stem": "1929.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time I was like 13 just walking around looking at the Germans and everything else.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the thing I remember most about that place-- and I know I wouldn't have survived there-- It was that if you went to the outhouse there--",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outhouse.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Washroom.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't want to use the word washroom because it wasn't a washroom.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was just a block house, wooden place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was covered literally with shit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean the walls, the floors, everything was covered was shit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had-- my head was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, they were everywhere on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You just-- you couldn't clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no sanitary condition period.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I'm sure that it would have been just the matter of a week or two, and I wouldn't have been able to survive because I don't think the food was anything there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I don't remember seeing my brother or my father there, although they probably were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And just a few weeks-- we were only there a couple of weeks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a very important town in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Russian army was there right on the heel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now again, I blank out with memory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were packed into trains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no memory.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably was soup and some salt, bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was just-- it was just the atmosphere there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just the, the helplessness of the other inmates.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think inmates is the right word.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I don't remember anybody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember that they would just drop down and the next morning they would die.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just be taken out, corpses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
